# Predefined Callback Structures

**API Collection**

CFSet provides some predefined callbacks for your convenience.

## Constants

- **kCFTypeSetCallBacks**
- **kCFCopyStringSetCallBacks**: Predefined [doc://com.apple.corefoundation/documentation/CoreFoundation/CFSetCallBacks] structure containing a set of callbacks  appropriate for use when the values in a set are all CFString objects. The retain callback makes an immutable copy of strings added to the set.
